"title": "9130: future, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9130: future, the",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's promises about the future are certain because it is under God's control. Christians should live on the basis that these promises, which focus on the return of Jesus Christ, will be fulfilled.</p>\n<h2>God controls the future</h2>\n<h3>God knows the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:19-Exod3:20\">EXO 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:21\">DEU 31:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:19\">2SA 7:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:17\">1CH 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:4\">PSA 139:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:9\">ISA 42:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10\">ISA 46:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:28\">DAN 2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>God can reveal the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:45\">DAN 2:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:13-Gen15:16\">GEN 15:13–15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:25\">GEN 41:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:15-1Sam9:16\">1SA 9:15–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:10\">2KI 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:19\">DAN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:14\">DAN 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:10\">ACT 18:9–18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:22-Acts27:24\">ACT 27:22–27:24</a></p>\n<h2>The future is unknown to human beings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:7\">ECC 8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:1\">PRO 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:22\">ECC 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:14\">ECC 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:14\">ECC 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:42-Matt24:43\">MAT 24:42–24:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22\">ACT 20:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14\">JAS 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>There is a future hope for believers</h2>\n<h3>It is based on God's promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:17\">JER 31:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:37\">PSA 37:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:18\">PRO 23:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:14\">PRO 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:15\">ISA 60:15</a></p>\n<h3>Future blessings are guaranteed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11\">JER 29:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:7\">GEN 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:3-Lev26:5\">LEV 26:3–26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:2\">DEU 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9\">DEU 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:23\">ISA 30:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:23\">ISA 65:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13\">AMO 9:13</a></p>\n<h3>Future blessings are superior to present experiences</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:21-Phil1:23\">PHP 1:21–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:17-Gen22:18\">GEN 22:17–22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18-Rom8:25\">ROM 8:18–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Key aspects of future hope</h2>\n<h3>Believers will go to heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:22\">LUK 16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1\">2CO 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ will come again</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:11\">ACT 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13\">DAN 7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20\">PHP 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16\">1TH 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1\">2TH 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:8\">JAS 5:8</a></p>\n<h3>The dead will rise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:52\">1CO 15:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28-John5:29\">JHN 5:28–5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:39-John6:40\">JHN 6:39–6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:15\">ACT 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:4-Rev20:5\">REV 20:4–20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">REV 20:12</a></p>\n<h3>Final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:12\">PSA 62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:32\">MAT 25:31–25:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:7\">2PE 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:17\">1JN 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:14-Jude1:15\">JUD 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:13\">REV 20:13</a></p>\n<h3>The devil and evil will be destroyed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:7-Isa25:8\">ISA 25:7–25:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">2TH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">REV 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:18\">REV 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20-Rev19:21\">REV 19:20–19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's kingdom will be fully established</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:9\">ZEC 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24\">1CO 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:5\">REV 21:1–21:5</a></p>\n<h2>Believers' responsibility towards future generations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:6-Josh4:7\">JOS 4:6–4:7</a></strong> <em>The twelve stones taken from the bed of the river Jordan is one of several instances where God's people are told to preserve memorials of present blessings for the sake of future generations.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:25-Exod12:27\">EXO 12:25–12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:32-Exod16:33\">EXO 16:32–16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:20-Deut6:21\">DEU 6:20–6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:21-Josh4:22\">JOS 4:21–4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:27\">JOS 22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:30\">PSA 22:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:17\">PSA 45:17</a></p>\n<h2>Proper attitudes towards the future</h2>\n<h3>Looking forwards rather than backwards</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:13–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:17\">GEN 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:18-Isa43:19\">ISA 43:18–43:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:2\">COL 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:2\">HEB 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h3>Having perseverance and faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9\">GAL 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6-Heb11:8\">HEB 11:6–11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:17-Heb11:19\">HEB 11:17–11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:11\">REV 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Avoiding occult predictions and false prophecies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:9\">JER 27:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:25-Isa44:26\">ISA 44:25–44:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:8\">JER 29:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:3-Ezek13:7\">EZK 13:3–13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16-Acts16:18\">ACT 16:16–16:18</a></p>",
